             was indicted for <rs id="t18211205-52-off309" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18211205-52-off309" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18211205-52-off309" type="offenceSubcategory" value="burglary"></interp>
               burglariously breaking and entering the dwelling-house of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18211205-52-victim633" type="victimName">
                           William 
                           Ord
                        <interp inst="t18211205-52-victim633" type="surname" value="Ord"></interp>
